{"tid":2211441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男警涉與毒販交易 情報科同袍指過程快如握手","createTime":"2020-09-21T06:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T10:17:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc584fe168f6a259e7e9aaf62e5910f1ee4ad01","tid":2211441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"男警陳天賜去年休班期間疑在屋苑平台與毒販交易，全程遭同袍在高位監視，其後被截查，發現疑身藏約值660元的K毒。警方同日在屋苑商場拘捕涉案女子。兩人分別被控藏毒及販毒。<strong><span class=\"red\">男警早前因「冇開信箱」及「瞓咗」等理由而缺席聆訊</span></strong>，及後又被指確診感染武漢肺炎；案件歷經諸多阻滯，至今早終於開審。負責監視的警員獲安排在屏風後作供，供稱目擊被告男警與他人交收，過程快如握手。<br />\n<br />\n兩名男女被告為陳天賜（47歲）及阮嘉欣，原本分案被控。陳面對一項藏毒罪，阮則面對一項販毒罪，兩人被控於去年2月21日在新屯門中心3座地下電梯大堂犯案，涉及兩個小袋共重1.13克的氯胺酮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/GTQYX6XRAVBWNNDLZVNL5PMB6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FGTQYX6XRAVBWNNDLZVNL5PMB6M%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b83587d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FGTQYX6XRAVBWNNDLZVNL5PMB6M%2F&h=488fb24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/GTQYX6XRAVBWNNDLZVNL5PMB6M/</a>"},{"pid":"59783c10f9deb81544d741084a6d58b7b4660069","tid":2211441,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊完全冇紀律 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1b65b9717bc51459da4a4703d61e0b6378b644","tid":2211441,"uid":271516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"有DOJ沒事兒"},{"pid":"047394cecb5ba4da8500153292d09eff576b436a","tid":2211441,"uid":68080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"撤控咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ce02431243f8b3bbcff250d20c4204ba62f5c0","tid":2211441,"uid":365024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2